long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tab Manager. 
Tabulous is a plug-in for managing chrome histories. It can generate tabs snapshots with one click and keep numbers of snapshot for you to switch back to a working state in the future.

Tabulous是一款用于管理chrome访问记录的插件。它可以一键生成tabs快照，保留任意多个快照记录，用于您在将来快速切换回到某一个工作状态。
